                    <h2>
                        <u>Population growth</u>
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        Melbourne is a great city and one of the fastest growing cities. everyone wants to live here and enjoy its serenity. Melbourne’s population has grown substantially from past 25 years. According to Victorian state government and Australian Bureau of statistics, Melbourne is fastest growing city in Australia and Victoria’s population is expected to almost double by 2051. Since 2001, Melbourne has added 1.5 million new residents. And also have declared that over the next 50 years, the population of Melbourne and surrounding suburbs can from 4.6 Million to 8 Million.
                        And over next few years it is anticipated to reach over 10 million. With current water levels and water sources it will be a tedious job to provide water to all the residents of Melbourne and surrounding areas.
                    </p>
